Let it not, Brutus. 
BRUTUS 
Every thing is well. 
60 
CASSIUS 
Good night, my lord. 
BRUTUS 
Good night, good brother. 
TITINIUS  Good night, Lord Brutus. 
BRUTUS 
Farewell, every one. 
